{
  "stem": "14737.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Next day, in the morning-- usually used to come in the morning-- and I see in the wagon, they take out a few dead from here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I didn't know where they put them, how they put them, where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was probably on a-- on a-- on a larger piece.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Not far was also where they put on a-- on a pile dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Those who were laying on the floor were laying, but from the room they wanted take out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and he drags me down from-- from that and starts to-- two of them-- starts to drag me also to this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the wagon were laying already two dead people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was still alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was telling, but I'm-- in Hungarian-- [HUNGARIAN], he says, I still am alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was also, but he couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He puts me on also on that wagon, like among this, I know for sure brings me there to the-- to that pile.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As he goes with his wagon, I somehow-- one foot of mine was somehow wasn't-- didn't fit in, and my foot somehow was over leaning-- I didn't have the strength-- and somehow from that wagon, I slipped, and not voluntarily, and I fell on the floor, and he continued to go further.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't pay attention.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was also among those dead there, so probably didn't pay attention to come back and take me again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that point, a man--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- no, not involuntarily slipped out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was somehow-- there was this small wagon, and I was laying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't put me on the right way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't put me on the right way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't fit me in that I should be among these people.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
